@startuml
title Patron State - Estados simples con choices de Django

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

class Order {
  +status
  +payment_status
  +change_status(new_status, new_payment_status, note)
}

class StockReservation {
  +status
  +reserve()
  +expire()
  +release()
}

enum OrderStatus {
  pending
  processing
  completed
  cancelled
}

enum PaymentStatus {
  pending
  paid
  failed
  refunded
}

enum ReservationStatus {
  reserved
  expired
  released
}

Order --> OrderStatus : choices
Order --> PaymentStatus : choices
StockReservation --> ReservationStatus : choices

Order "1" *-- "0..*" StockReservation : reservas

note right of Order
Inspirado en GoF State:
las fases del pedido se controlan
con valores permitidos.
No usa clases de estado separadas.
end note

note right of StockReservation
La reserva cambia de fase
mediante metodos explicitos.
end note

@enduml
